There are [a few types exception that extend `AuthException`](https://github.com/aws-amplify/amplify-android/search?q=%22extends+AuthException%22).

As in [this answer](https://stackoverflow.com/a/48213377/695787), I suggest is to exhaust those types using a `when` construct. Paraphrasing:
```kotlin
when (error) {
    is SessionUnavailableOfflineException -&gt; doSomething()
    is InvalidAccountTypeException -&gt; doSomethingElse()
    // etc.
}
